General.Name: ITAB Shop Concept AB ser. B
General.Description: ITAB Shop Concept AB (publ) provides solution design, customized shop fittings, checkouts, consumer flow solutions, professional lighting systems, and digitally interactive solutions for the physical stores. It offers checkouts and self-service systems; click and collect, an automated and convenient online delivery option; consumer and colleague safety systems; consumer interaction systems; security gates for entrance and exit; queue management systems; standard fittings and accessories; and retail lighting products. The company also provides solution design; services to consolidate goods not for resale; installation and assembly services for retail concepts; and after-care and maintenance services. It serves grocery, home improvements, fashion, consumer electronics, cafes and service stations, pharmacy, and health and beauty customers. The company operates in Italy, the United Kingdom, Germany, Norway, Sweden, Finland, France, the Czech Republic, the Netherlands, Denmark, the United States, Poland, Spain, Lithuania, Argentina, and internationally. ITAB Shop Concept AB (publ) was incorporated in 1987 and is headquartered in Jönköping, Sweden.
